    },
    {
      "id": "626fc97ce5172d0000f1769d",
      "text": " Scrapboxに保存することを「[scrapする]」と言うことがある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1651493244,
      "updated": 1727214365
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca3ee5172d0000f43abc",
      "text": " 　公式も使っている",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493438,
      "updated": 1651493442
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca2ee5172d0000f43aba",
      "text": "  　[https://gyazo.com/1990b68d7d5ea67de420dc8f5f21a277]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493423,
      "updated": 1651493442
    },
    {
      "id": "626fca2de5172d0000f43ab9",
      "text": " が、scrapにそういう意味はないのかも？[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493421,
      "updated": 1651493421
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc9b9e5172d0000f176a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493305,
      "updated": 1651493334
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc9d6e5172d0000f176a1",
      "text": "> 動詞 他動詞",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493334,
      "updated": 1651493336
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc9d8e5172d0000f176a2",
      "text": "> (scrapped; scrap・ping)",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493336,
      "updated": 1651493336
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc9d8e5172d0000f176a3",
      "text": "> 1〈…を〉くずとして捨てる，[くず鉄]にする.",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1651493336,
      "updated": 1727214372
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc9d8e5172d0000f176a4",
      "text": "> scrap an old car 古くなった自動車をスクラップにする.",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493336,
      "updated": 1651493336
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc9d8e5172d0000f176a5",
      "text": "> 2〈計画などを〉やめにする，ほごにする.",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493336,
      "updated": 1651493336
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc97ce5172d0000f1769e",
      "text": "[https://ejje.weblio.jp/content/scrap scrapの意味・使い方・読み方 | Weblio英和辞書]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493244,
      "updated": 1651493344
    },
    {
      "id": "626fc9e0e5172d0000f176a7",
      "text": "　Scrapboxを「[屑箱]」と訳すなら、Scrap=「屑として捨てる」で通じるけども[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493344,
      "updated": 1651493600
    },
    {
      "id": "626fcabce5172d0000f43abd",
      "text": "　　皮肉が効きすぎている気がするｗ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1651493564,
      "updated": 1651493590
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddc3f20000000000188b06",
